    <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
    <ul>
        <li>
            <strong>How much does it cost to list properties as an agent on SWRELS.COM?</strong><br />The annual fee for membership is located on the agent sign-up page. You will be notified of your renewal date one week prior to automatic renewal. During this week you will need to update any changes to your profile and payment information. You may also cancel your listings at this time and choose not to renew.
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>What are keywords?</strong><br />Keywords allow agents and consumers to search real estate by keywords. Click here for a list of keywords.
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Will there be any type of promotions for sign up as an agent?</strong><br />Yes! From time to time promotions will be established. Promotions may start or end without notice.
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>How will the site be promoted as to ensure getting it in front of agents and consumers?</strong><br />Several methods will be used, Search Engine Optimization, real estate agents and offices to put a link (www.swrels.com) on their web sites. Also other avenues will be newspaper, television, and bill boards. A large part of proceeds will be invested to get this site known throughout the nation.
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>What must I do to be able to list properties on this web site?</strong><br />First you have to be an active real estate agent in good standing in the state you are licensed. You do not, however, have to be a member of any other local or state board. Click sign up on the home page and follow the instructions on each page then save your information. Your status will be verified and approved; you will be notified via email. Your information is safe and secure on SWRELS.COM.
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>What happens to the information in my profile?</strong><br />Your information is stored for you to view and update whenever you need it. Your information is safe and secure and is never shared with third parties. Credit or debit card info only stores the last four digits. Your complete number is never seen by anyone.
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Will agents be able to have an input?</strong><br />Yes. We encourage suggestions and ideas. Click the "feedback" link on the agent page to give input on a regular basis. Every idea or suggestion will be read and analyzed. If it is feasible, then SWERLS.com will endeavor to incorporate that idea into the system.
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Will SWRELS.com have opportunities for employment?</strong><br />SWRELS.com is planning to provide sources of creating jobs in many areas. Stay in touch with the site for announcements as we expand. We will post those opportunities on the site along with contact information.
        </li>
    </ul>
